Axel.

09:02.237 --> 09:03.804
Oh, shit.

09:31.483 --> 09:33.050
...Come on!

09:33.094 --> 09:34.661
Run, run, run!

09:34.704 --> 09:36.793
You gotta be kidding me?

10:13.134 --> 10:14.701
Come on!

10:14.744 --> 10:16.137
Let's go!

10:17.921 --> 10:19.706
Hurry up!

10:21.533 --> 10:22.883
Shit!

10:26.713 --> 10:27.714
Oh my god!

10:28.802 --> 10:29.803
Grab your shit and go!

10:29.846 --> 10:32.066
Get outta here, now!

10:39.639 --> 10:40.901
Run now! Go!

10:48.648 --> 10:50.214
Go, run, run, run!

10:50.258 --> 10:51.825
Go, go, go, go!

